name: Orchard.angularjs
tagline: All resources distributed as part of the latest stable AngularJS toolkit in an Orchard module package
body:
### Get it from the Orchard gallery!
https://gallery.orchardproject.net/List/Modules/Orchard.Module.Orchard.AngularJS

### Authors and Contributors
I cannot take any credit for the great work done by the Google team! This project is only an Orchard module package around the AngularJS scripts.

### Support or Contact
If you have trouble with the package in Orchard, you can find me @kroonwijk.
